<CL>
1 e5 cha-pou-lang5 beh khi3 tiuN7-lang5 tau, saN-a2-khou3 chheng7 ho2-se3, tu2-leh chheng7 in bou2 ka7 i be2 e5 hit-siang sin phoe5-e5. Chheng7 chiaN5 ku2 chheng7 be7 loh8-khi3, to7 khi3-chhoah-chhoah me7 in bou2 kong2: “Ho2 an5--e5 m7 an5, be2 kah chiah an5 beh chhong3-siaN2?” 
In bou2 thiaN liau2-au7, ma7 bo5 ho2 siaN-sau3 an2-ni ka7 in3 to3-tng2-khi3: “Ho2 toa7--e5 m7 toa7, kan-na7 toa7 hit-ki kha u7 siaN2 lou7-iong7.” 
</CL>
<HL>

一個查甫人beh去丈人兜，衫仔褲穿好勢，tu2-leh穿in某ka7伊買e5 hit雙新皮鞋。穿誠久穿be7落去，to7氣chhoah-chhoah罵in某講：「好an5--e5 m7 an5,買kah chiah an5 beh創啥？」
In某聽了後，ma7無好聲嗽an2-ni ka7應倒轉去：「好大--e5 m7大，kan-na7大hit支腳有啥路用。」
</HL>